Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.39,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(275,0)\blur1..5\pos(1470,890)}反省！指导室
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}---Text---
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为他们计划在校内偷东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因此正在受到处分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:09.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是啦…果然是会被退学之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:12.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不…他们被送去生活指导室了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:14.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}生活指导室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:15.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们…正在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:17.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接受着特别的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对违反了校规的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:23.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我会让你们对自己身为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}骄傲的本校学生这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:27.49,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}变得更有自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.39,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然我的眷属基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一直都处于饥饿状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这里是个特别的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以不会吃掉大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:10.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能会让它们钻进各式各样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像是耳朵或嘴巴之类而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:21.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有个超级不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妾身也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:25.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总之 遇到他们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:28.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}记得要非常 非常温柔的对待他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:29.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}特别是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:32.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谭雅·冯·提古雷查夫少校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的要拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我会在精神层面上好好锻炼他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感觉彼此的想法并没有对上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}逗之助的饲料要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我很担心你们两个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对了 你们到底受到了怎么样的指导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是恐怖类型的 还是快乐类型的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个快回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们那个表情到底是发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}指导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那才不是什么指导呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:08.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}黑色的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.71,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一只接着一只的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.41,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你…你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:13.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}达克妮丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.75,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿…阿克娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}粘在你头发上的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就没有什么方法能救他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才半天而已就变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真他们的心灵会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:48.88,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和很多黑色生物一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听起来并没有很恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那可是小小的黑色恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.47,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以超夸张的数量在身边爬来爬去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.93,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然嘴巴上这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但你该不会其实并不讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:02.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和整群的小型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:03.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}待在一起之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.09,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那到底要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:08.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太无情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.09,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经没有什么我们能做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昴 不然我们去找雷鲁根老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}求情看看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好主意 爱蜜莉雅碳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以麻烦两位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 虽然不知道可以做到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:27.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我们会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:34.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有可能减轻对大家的处分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.83,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}多…多么好的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和那个披着幼女外表的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完全不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:50.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果做了一些「良好行为」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}应该就很有可能减轻对他们的处分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「良好行为」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 「良好行为」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.01,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也会再和校长先生说说看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}爱蜜莉雅君 真的是 天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎…怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯 老师说如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:18.45,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做了一些良好行为的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:21.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}应该就可以减轻对他们的处分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}良好行为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:24.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还满难的耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}良好行为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.26,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样的话不是满简单的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.39,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你还满有自信的嘛 惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下一堂课是化学实验对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:40.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你该不会在盘算什么不好的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:46.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么…就让我们开始实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}女孩 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请会使用火系魔法的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:58.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把酒精灯点着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.71,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Fire ball
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谁来点火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我来拜托微精灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}逗之助刚刚喷火了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}逗之助可是猫耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么可能会喷火嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}与其关心那个 这边要开始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.92,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾名为惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们这些家伙在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谭雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然我能明白你身为风纪委员的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.39,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是今天就让他们放手去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.60,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们也打算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用自己的方式帮助和真他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是如果发生问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他们也会被送去生活指导室的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:48.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}罗兹瓦尔老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也默认这个状况了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.16,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是这样吧 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聪明如罗兹瓦尔老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不可能没注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对不起 点酒精灯失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果是失败那就没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对吧 罗兹亲老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.95,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}失败的话就没办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但虽然说是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:38.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这状况好像有点惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.24,0:07:46.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那两个人会如何处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.22,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像听到了什么很大的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}听声音应该是水流声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且好像越来越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}往这个校长室来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:06.45,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且这里还有你私藏的雪茄…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.45,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.41,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.01,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}校长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果我们能解决水的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可以解除对我们的惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赏罚分明是世界的常理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真 阿克娅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我吧 长脸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是肯尼希啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:33.95,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诺伊曼 格兰兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.12,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}张开护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:39.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快把收集好的水灌进我的护盾里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:42.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是现在 阿克娅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.29,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我可是水之女神喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 交给你了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宴会女神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:55.45,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就让你们看看水之女神的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我本来觉得她是个头脑怪怪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但看来实力是货真价实的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:04.31,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是…是女神…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}覆水 难收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然还是宴会用的才艺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:22.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}禁闭已经被解除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都做了「良好行为」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}惠惠可是做了「不良行为」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我听不懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总之 都是多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果真的学乖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就请不要再违反校规了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}惠惠小姐 也很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要道谢就去跟你们队长大人说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为那时候她身为风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却没有阻止我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好 诺伊曼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那你代表我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去道个谢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:57.90,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:01.46,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}罗兹瓦尔老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀 是恐怖公老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}以结果而言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.71,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样也让班上同学更团结了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能这样一直顺利下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:15.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如何 晚一点要一起共进下午茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请容我拒绝
